• A rename input box should appear when clicking the rename icon.
• The new name should be saved instantly in the chat history list.
• No special characters should be allowed except (_ - .).
• If an empty name is entered, an error message should appear.
• If the name exceeds the character limit, a validation message should be displayed.
• If the user presses Esc, the chat name should remain unchanged.
• The rename icon should be clearly visible and clickable.

